data: Supporting business growth and competitiveness by delivering university-accredited management qualifications to employees.

Multi-agency partnership to support engagement of 16-24 year olds who are NEET in to education, training or employment. Ensuring that young people gain the appropriate holistic support to achieve the skills and qualifications required to enter sustained employment including the skills needed for economic growth across the region.
